programme.desc: While Grizzy struggles to pick coconuts that are too high up, the Lemmings find a magic conch.

programme.title: Clarence
programme.desc: Gilben's newly sprouted peach fuzz sparks a discussion about puberty that ultimately convinces Clarence to act more like an adult.

programme.title: Mechamato
programme.desc: Amato and Pian try to rehabilitate the bad robots but an accident gives the bad robot Scarescrew a chance to escape.

programme.title: Mr Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mrs. Wicket demands that Bean drives her and Miss Wince to their booked spa retreat; and wait outside in the car until they’re done.

programme.title: We Bare Bears

programme.title: The Amazing World Of Gumball

programme.desc: Robin still regrets not being able to find an Easter egg when he was a kid, so the Titans head to Gotham to solve this mystery.

programme.title: The White Storm 2: Drug Lords
programme.desc: In this epic action-thriller starring Andy Lau and Louis Koo, the two award-winning best actors star on opposing sides of a drug war. As a bounty of $100 million Hong Kong dollars is made to hunt down the biggest drug dealer in the city, Hong Kong becomes the battleground for the fight between good and evil.

programme.title: You are the One
programme.desc: A talented rogue trader experiences a 180-degree change in life when he encounters a girl who does not believe good things will happen to her. Will they fall in love? It seems like a Cinderella’s adventure has just begun!

programme.title: See You Tomorrow
programme.desc: In this chaotic world, every city has its own "navigators" who can help solve various relationship issues. Bar owner Chen and his partner Guan are legendary navigators, but in the process of helping a girl Xiao Yu, they must also face their own problems in an epic act of self-discovery that brings their lives from towering highs to withering lows.

programme.title: Destiny's Champion
programme.desc: An aging fighter relives the mistakes of his violent past through a poor and streetwise kid, who severely injures his nemesis during a battle to win a girl's heart.

programme.title: A Murder Erased
programme.desc: Police officer Choi is assigned to a death scene investigation where the deceased body had laid undiscovered for eight years. A prosecutor joins the investigation after Choi has identified the suspect, and finds Choi’s actions suspicious when all manner of inconsistencies come to light from his statement...

programme.title: Hong Kong Family
programme.desc: Eight years ago, the family in a Hakka-walled village was torn apart during a combative winter solstice dinner. Eight years later, their cousin returns home from England and seeks to reunite the family for another winter solstice dinner. While things seem to be falling apart, this dinner may well be an opportunity to mend relations.

programme.title: The Battle at Lake Changjin
programme.desc: Set in the winter of 1950, a pivotal battle during the Korean war begins at the freezing Lake Changjin region. Facing extreme cold, hunger and weaker weapons, the Chinese troops nonetheless forge ahead, fearless and determined, eventually winning a critical victory against the US aggression and aid Korea in the war.

programme.title: Black Ransom
programme.desc: Mann, an accomplished police officer, has allowed his career to wane after his wife was murdered by the mafia. However, Mann is forced to return to his former glory when he is assigned to investigate a former police inspector suspected to be kidnapping mafia bosses and demanding ransoms in exchange for their lives.

programme.title: Marrying Mr Perfect
programme.desc: Winnie is dumped by her boyfriend in her late twenties and unknowingly meets Koo, a ruthless tycoon in business and a playboy. Koo temporarily switches identities with his driver for security reason and falls for Winnie as she is the first girl to love him for who he is. What will happen when Winnie know Koo’s real identity?

programme.title: Miao Miao
programme.desc: Miao Miao is an awkward young beauty who nevertheless enchants her outgoing classmate Xiao Ai. As Xiao Ai’s feelings for Miao Miao grows from friendship to something more, Miao Miao discovers her own burgeoning attraction to a sullen CD store owner, and quietly pursues him.

programme.title: The Silent War
programme.desc: After the Chinese Civil War, 701 Bureau continues to monitor the coded transmissions between rebel forces. When radio frequencies used by the opponent disappear suddenly, Agent Zhang asks Ho, a blind piano tuner with exceptional hearing, to help find the transmission signals. Can Ho find the missing signals and foil a possible assassination plot?

programme.title: Detective Vs. Sleuths
programme.desc: Hong Kong is rocked by a series of cold-blooded murders whose victims are runaway suspects of unsolved cases. The group of killers calls themselves “The Chosen Sleuths". Former top detective Lee vows to bring the brutal killers to justice and prove himself to be the real “Chosen Sleuth” instead of a lunatic.

programme.title: Those Were the Days
programme.desc: Director Wong despises Cantonese movies of the 60s, but accidentally travels back in time to that movie set. He meets Director Chu, who tells him he can return to modern time if someone likes the film he makes. Wong meets four classic movie stars and invites them to star in his new film, but it flops unexpectedly. Can Wong return to the present?

programme.title: Legally Declared Dead
programme.desc: Insurance agent Sean visits Tak and Ling's home to follow up on a case and is shocked to see their son's corpse hanging above him. He suspects them of murdering their son to claim the insurance money and decides to launch his own investigation. As he becomes obsessed over their guilt, his kind nature is used against him by the real perpetrator.

programme.title: Find Your Voice
programme.desc: The “passion choir pilot program” trains students from three underperforming schools’ choir to participate in an inter-school choral competition. While it seems impossible, a renowned conductor, Yim Tsz Long, unexpectedly agrees to lead the choir. Will the “passion choir” and Maestro Yim complete this impossible mission and win the competition?

programme.title: Dummy Mommy, without a Baby
programme.desc: Fong Lai Kuen works at an advertising agency but is about to be sacked by her boss after offending him. She pretends to be pregnant so that the company cannot fire her, according to the labour law. Since then, Fong receives much care and love from her colleagues and begins to feel guilty about her lie as things develop out of her expectations.

programme.title: Lonely Eighteen
programme.desc: Set in the 1980s Hong Kong, Elaine and her best friend Ying enter the entertainment industry hoping to change their fates from poverty. Ying soon becomes a popular porn star but Elaine is lost between being her true self and an actress. When show business declines after a decade, their choices lead them to two different paths in life.

programme.title: Shark Busters
programme.desc: During the financial crisis, a vast majority of Hong Kong people experience difficulties in repaying debts. During this time, loan sharks use ruthless ways to force debtors to repay their loans and it is up to Officer Lee and his underground team to hunt down the head of this illegal organization.

programme.title: Just 1 Day
programme.desc: Mosaic, an urban sketcher, is suffering from ALS and wants to create some fond memories as his condition worsens. When Mosaic reunites with his old classmate Angelfish, whom he has a crush on since primary school, he asks her to fulfill his one last wish by becoming his girlfriend for just one day. Will Angelfish say “yes”?

programme.title: Death Stranding
programme.desc: To overhaul the underground gambling industry, the police join hands with the gambling association to crack down on illegal casinos. They auction off new casino licenses to regulate the industry, but this results in an upheaval in the gambling world, unveiling the hidden interests and secrets while sparking conflicts between gangs...

programme.title: Life Must Go On
programme.desc: When the “midnight gymnasium” programme for wayward teenage girls is at funding risk, social worker Yanki puts together a dodgeball team to compete in a match and save it. With an ex-star athlete John as the coach, the girls realize they must face their problems and overcome their challenges instead of dodging them. Can they finally win the match?

programme.title: Touch of the Light
programme.desc: A blind but talented pianist Siang encounters an unrecognized but skilful dancer Chieh. Chieh is attracted to the courageous Siang while Siang is fascinated by the adventurous Chieh. Their friendship grows as Siang and Chieh pursue their dreams together. Sandrine Pinna was awarded Best Actress for her role as Chieh in the 2012 Taipei Film Festival.

programme.title: Caught in Time
programme.desc: Based on true events, Detective Zhong Cheng leads a task force in pursuit of Eagle, a criminal gang led by Zhang Sun. Highly methodical and disciplined, the gang manages to avoid capture after each heist. A decade later, the need to stop Eagle is more urgent than ever when Zhong Cheng realizes that his time is almost up to solve the case.

programme.title: My Indian Boyfriend
programme.desc: This is a love story between a Hong Kong girl and an Indian boy and is the first Bollywood movie to be made in Hong Kong. It encapsulates the conflicts caused by discrimination as well as differences in social-cultural background, lifestyle and family values between the races. The movie also combines tears, joy and laughter with song and dance.

programme.title: My Kung Fu Sweetheart
programme.desc: Phoenix’s (Cecilia Cheung) parents are martial arts superheroes, who hide their true identities while ferreting out evil martial artists. Phoenix gets the go-ahead to train in the misty mountains, where she learns of her all-important romantic destiny...

programme.title: Bursting Point
programme.desc: Senior Inspector Bang sends Officer Ming undercover in a drug cartel to displace drug lord Yang. A failed raid triggers Yang's rage for revenge. Meanwhile, drug maker Ying Xiu is forced to cooperate with the police and sets a trap for Yang. The battle between the police and the drug cartel has just begun!

programme.title: Special Couple
programme.desc: Gu works in London but is set to be deported back to China due to problems of his visa. His best friend, Jin, is a UK citizen and suggests disguising as a couple with Gu to secure his stay. Everything goes well until Gu falls for his neighbour and Jin’s parents pay a surprise visit. The two men begin to doubt if they should tell the truth.

programme.title: The Sparring Partner
programme.desc: Adapted from a sensational 2013 parricide in Hong Kong, a young man partners with his friend to murder and dismember his parents. Pleading not guilty, the defendants play the devil and idiot game, while the defense attorneys turn on each other. Meanwhile, heated debates emerge inside the jury room, where nine jurors grapple with the truth.

programme.title: Vanguard
programme.desc: A businessman Qin Guo Li is being kidnapped in London and his daughter is also in danger. The international security team, Vanguard, is hired to rescue them. Tang Huan Ting, the founder, gathers an elite team to track them down across countries, from London to Africa and Dubai. In the process, they also discover another dangerous conspiracy.

programme.title: A Guilty Conscience
programme.desc: Due to the negligence of sharp-tongued barrister Adrian, his innocent client is convicted of murder and sentenced to 17 years in jail. An opportunity to appeal the case and free his client arises a few years later, but in order to right his wrong, he must fight against one of the most powerful families in Hong Kong for justice to prevail.

programme.title: Once Upon a Time in Hong Kong
programme.desc: This is a story of ICAC investigators fighting against rampant corruption in early 1970s’ Hong Kong. A police sergeant teams up with a triad boss to make billions of dollars in bribes. As a lawyer joins his friend in ICAC to investigate their collusion and fight against corruption, the battle between the righteous and the wicked has just begun.

programme.title: Love Never Ends
programme.desc: An empty-nest elderly man and a widowed elderly woman who collects scrap, meet unexpectedly and gradually develop feelings for each other. An elderly couple whose wife suffers from a serious illness, makes a living by selling scrap. Both these elderly couples fall deeply in love and prove that love never ends, even if there is no tomorrow!

programme.title: Bursting Point
programme.desc: Senior Inspector Bang sends Officer Ming undercover in a drug cartel to displace drug lord Yang. A failed raid triggers Yang's rage for revenge. Meanwhile, drug maker Ying Xiu is forced to cooperate with the police and sets a trap for Yang. The battle between the police and the drug cartel has just begun!

programme.title: Men Suddenly in Love
programme.desc: Five high-school alumni - councilor Ng Yuk Yan, actor Cheung Chau Wan, gynecologist Fu Mo Sum, feng shui master Szeto Kei Fung, and dance coach Charlie Lam - get together to throw a birthday party for their respected teacher Mr. Chu, who enlightened them about the birds and the bees. Five delectable young models appear at the party, during which the 80-year-old educator gets too excited and unfortunately kicks the bucket - but not before telling his pupils to fulfill his last wish and get a little naughty! The quintet of married men then takes it upon themselves to conquer the babes, all the while trying to evade the watchful eye of their wives.

programme.title: Turns We Take
programme.desc: A spicy hot pot restaurant in Northeast China serves different types of customers every day. Amongst them are a sweet young couple, two wayward young men and a taxi driver. Despite being complete strangers to each other, their lives are intertwined by a traffic accident…

programme.title: Leio
programme.desc: An ex-singer Kao returns to his hometown for a funeral and takes part in a water drilling contest to save his drought-stricken hometown, as well as to win a million dollar cash prize. However, what Kao and other contestants do not realize is that there is a fierce and deadly beast lurking underground who wants to eat them all!

programme.title: The Sunny Side of the Street
programme.desc: Hassan is a Pakistani refugee boy whose father has died in a car accident. A local taxi driver, Yat, then helps him flee Hong Kong. In the process, the two gradually develop a father-son relationship, until Hassan discovers the shocking truth about his father’s death…

programme.title: Love is Blind, Hate Too
programme.desc: Bo lost her eye sight in a serious car accident a year ago. One day, she is left alone at home when her husband is away on a work trip. An intruder enters Bo's house and takes her hostage. As Bo tries to survive his mental and psychological torture, she discovers her husband's secret which is related to the accident leading to her blindness…

programme.title: Unleashed
programme.desc: Fok Kit is the hottest underground boxer with unbeatable records. To save their boxing studio from being sold, he must win the fight against Shaolin who is known as "Killing Machine". Fok Kit is defeated and badly hurt in the fight, which is a set-up by Lok, who wants to take revenge on Fok Kit’s master, Debo.

programme.desc: Set in the 1980s Hong Kong, Elaine and her best friend Ying enter the entertainment industry hoping to change their fates from poverty. Ying soon becomes a popular porn star but Elaine is lost between being her true self and an actress. When show business declines after a decade, their choices lead them to two different paths in life.

programme.title: Shark Busters
programme.desc: During the financial crisis, a vast majority of Hong Kong people experience difficulties in repaying debts. During this time, loan sharks use ruthless ways to force debtors to repay their loans and it is up to Officer Lee and his underground team to hunt down the head of this illegal organization.

programme.title: Just 1 Day
programme.desc: Mosaic, an urban sketcher, is suffering from ALS and wants to create some fond memories as his condition worsens. When Mosaic reunites with his old classmate Angelfish, whom he has a crush on since primary school, he asks her to fulfill his one last wish by becoming his girlfriend for just one day. Will Angelfish say “yes”?

programme.title: Death Stranding
programme.desc: To overhaul the underground gambling industry, the police join hands with the gambling association to crack down on illegal casinos. They auction off new casino licenses to regulate the industry, but this results in an upheaval in the gambling world, unveiling the hidden interests and secrets while sparking conflicts between gangs...

programme.title: Life Must Go On
programme.desc: When the “midnight gymnasium” programme for wayward teenage girls is at funding risk, social worker Yanki puts together a dodgeball team to compete in a match and save it. With an ex-star athlete John as the coach, the girls realize they must face their problems and overcome their challenges instead of dodging them. Can they finally win the match?

programme.title: Touch of the Light
programme.desc: A blind but talented pianist Siang encounters an unrecognized but skilful dancer Chieh. Chieh is attracted to the courageous Siang while Siang is fascinated by the adventurous Chieh. Their friendship grows as Siang and Chieh pursue their dreams together. Sandrine Pinna was awarded Best Actress for her role as Chieh in the 2012 Taipei Film Festival.

programme.title: Caught in Time
programme.desc: Based on true events, Detective Zhong Cheng leads a task force in pursuit of Eagle, a criminal gang led by Zhang Sun. Highly methodical and disciplined, the gang manages to avoid capture after each heist. A decade later, the need to stop Eagle is more urgent than ever when Zhong Cheng realizes that his time is almost up to solve the case.

programme.title: My Indian Boyfriend
programme.desc: This is a love story between a Hong Kong girl and an Indian boy and is the first Bollywood movie to be made in Hong Kong. It encapsulates the conflicts caused by discrimination as well as differences in social-cultural background, lifestyle and family values between the races. The movie also combines tears, joy and laughter with song and dance.

programme.title: My Kung Fu Sweetheart
programme.desc: Phoenix’s (Cecilia Cheung) parents are martial arts superheroes, who hide their true identities while ferreting out evil martial artists. Phoenix gets the go-ahead to train in the misty mountains, where she learns of her all-important romantic destiny...

programme.title: Bursting Point
programme.desc: Senior Inspector Bang sends Officer Ming undercover in a drug cartel to displace drug lord Yang. A failed raid triggers Yang's rage for revenge. Meanwhile, drug maker Ying Xiu is forced to cooperate with the police and sets a trap for Yang. The battle between the police and the drug cartel has just begun!

programme.title: Special Couple
programme.desc: Gu works in London but is set to be deported back to China due to problems of his visa. His best friend, Jin, is a UK citizen and suggests disguising as a couple with Gu to secure his stay. Everything goes well until Gu falls for his neighbour and Jin’s parents pay a surprise visit. The two men begin to doubt if they should tell the truth.

programme.title: The Sparring Partner
programme.desc: Adapted from a sensational 2013 parricide in Hong Kong, a young man partners with his friend to murder and dismember his parents. Pleading not guilty, the defendants play the devil and idiot game, while the defense attorneys turn on each other. Meanwhile, heated debates emerge inside the jury room, where nine jurors grapple with the truth.

programme.title: Vanguard
programme.desc: A businessman Qin Guo Li is being kidnapped in London and his daughter is also in danger. The international security team, Vanguard, is hired to rescue them. Tang Huan Ting, the founder, gathers an elite team to track them down across countries, from London to Africa and Dubai. In the process, they also discover another dangerous conspiracy.

programme.title: A Guilty Conscience
programme.desc: Due to the negligence of sharp-tongued barrister Adrian, his innocent client is convicted of murder and sentenced to 17 years in jail. An opportunity to appeal the case and free his client arises a few years later, but in order to right his wrong, he must fight against one of the most powerful families in Hong Kong for justice to prevail.

programme.title: Once Upon a Time in Hong Kong
programme.desc: This is a story of ICAC investigators fighting against rampant corruption in early 1970s’ Hong Kong. A police sergeant teams up with a triad boss to make billions of dollars in bribes. As a lawyer joins his friend in ICAC to investigate their collusion and fight against corruption, the battle between the righteous and the wicked has just begun.

programme.title: Love Never Ends
programme.desc: An empty-nest elderly man and a widowed elderly woman who collects scrap, meet unexpectedly and gradually develop feelings for each other. An elderly couple whose wife suffers from a serious illness, makes a living by selling scrap. Both these elderly couples fall deeply in love and prove that love never ends, even if there is no tomorrow!

programme.title: Bursting Point
programme.desc: Senior Inspector Bang sends Officer Ming undercover in a drug cartel to displace drug lord Yang. A failed raid triggers Yang's rage for revenge. Meanwhile, drug maker Ying Xiu is forced to cooperate with the police and sets a trap for Yang. The battle between the police and the drug cartel has just begun!

programme.title: Men Suddenly in Love
programme.desc: Five high-school alumni - councilor Ng Yuk Yan, actor Cheung Chau Wan, gynecologist Fu Mo Sum, feng shui master Szeto Kei Fung, and dance coach Charlie Lam - get together to throw a birthday party for their respected teacher Mr. Chu, who enlightened them about the birds and the bees. Five delectable young models appear at the party, during which the 80-year-old educator gets too excited and unfortunately kicks the bucket - but not before telling his pupils to fulfill his last wish and get a little naughty! The quintet of married men then takes it upon themselves to conquer the babes, all the while trying to evade the watchful eye of their wives.

programme.title: Turns We Take
programme.desc: A spicy hot pot restaurant in Northeast China serves different types of customers every day. Amongst them are a sweet young couple, two wayward young men and a taxi driver. Despite being complete strangers to each other, their lives are intertwined by a traffic accident…

programme.title: Leio
programme.desc: An ex-singer Kao returns to his hometown for a funeral and takes part in a water drilling contest to save his drought-stricken hometown, as well as to win a million dollar cash prize. However, what Kao and other contestants do not realize is that there is a fierce and deadly beast lurking underground who wants to eat them all!

programme.title: The Sunny Side of the Street
programme.desc: Hassan is a Pakistani refugee boy whose father has died in a car accident. A local taxi driver, Yat, then helps him flee Hong Kong. In the process, the two gradually develop a father-son relationship, until Hassan discovers the shocking truth about his father’s death…

programme.title: Love is Blind, Hate Too
programme.desc: Bo lost her eye sight in a serious car accident a year ago. One day, she is left alone at home when her husband is away on a work trip. An intruder enters Bo's house and takes her hostage. As Bo tries to survive his mental and psychological torture, she discovers her husband's secret which is related to the accident leading to her blindness…

programme.title: Unleashed
programme.desc: Fok Kit is the hottest underground boxer with unbeatable records. To save their boxing studio from being sold, he must win the fight against Shaolin who is known as "Killing Machine". Fok Kit is defeated and badly hurt in the fight, which is a set-up by Lok, who wants to take revenge on Fok Kit’s master, Debo.

Tetapi ia bisa diselamatkan oleh pacarnya, Rachman sebelum ia terjerumus lebih jauh. Walaupun Yanti bekas pelacur, Rachman tetap menikahinya. Setelah belajar ilmu bela diri dari kakeknya Rachman, Yanti dan Rachman memutuskan untuk balas dendam kepada penjahat yang telah memperkosa Yanti

programme.title: Jangan Bilang Siapa-Siapa
programme.desc: Film ini menceritakan tentang Merry dan Andi yang baru menikah, namun sudah terjadi keanehan yang berujung kecurigaan di awal pernikahan mereka. Ditambah lagi saat Merry mendengar pembicaraan Andi dengan Kadir, pembantunya, dan akhirnya menjadi banyak salah paham.

programme.title: Bing Slamet Sibuk
programme.desc: Bercerita tentang Bing Slamet yang berhasil menaklukkan anak-anak keluarga Eddy Sud, orang yang mempekerjakannya, dengan kepandaiannya bernyanyi. Film ini juga sarat dengan lelucon dengan hadirnya grup Kwartet jaya.

programme.title: Kangen
programme.desc: Pertemuan dua remaja yang diawali kesinisan tanpa sengaja berubah menjadi sebuah hubungan romantis

programme.title: Hotline 666
programme.desc: Menceritakan tentang Erza yang terperangkap di sebuah rumah angker. Erza merupakan pengantar pizza, saat dia mengantaran pizza ke sebuah rumah an ternyata dihuni oleh Sandra, Miko, dan Dara. Sosok yang awalnya hanyalah rekaan Erza menjadi nyata. Pintu rumah itu tertutup secara gaib. Erza terkunci di dalamnya.

programme.title: Nazar
programme.desc: Cindy, cewek trendi yang benar-benar memenangkan mobil mewah dari undian tutup botol, mati-matian berusaha membatalkan nazar asal-asalannya.

programme.title: Berangkat
programme.desc: Kisah tiga sekawan, yakni, Jano, Joana, dan Dika yang masing-masing memiliki personality dan hobi yang berbeda. Mereka melakukan road trip ke Kawah Ijen dan dilanjutkan ke Bali. Bermodalkan VW Combi tua mereka menyusuri beberapa kota di Jawa dengan banyak cerita.

programme.title: Jones: Jomblo Ngenes
programme.desc: Noval jatuh cinta saat bertemu Astika. Tapi di antara suka dan bahagia, ada pula rasa sakit. Noval berkali-kali terjerumus di situasi di mana Astika memperdayainya. Astika meminta Noval berbuat dan berkata aneh-aneh di berbagai situasi menggelikan. Noval bisa saja menjauh, tapi pesona Atika membuatnya tak bisa meninggalkannya.

programme.title: Kuntilanak 2 (2019)
programme.desc: Di film pertama, Dinda berhasil lolos dari teror kuntilanak. Ia kemudian berniat menemui Karmila yang diyakini sebagai ibu kandungnya. Sialnya, Dinda yang berangkat bersama adik dan temannya malah terjebak dalam rumah di tengah hutan. Kejanggalan mulai terjadi di rumah tersebut. Dinda harus kembali berhadapan dengan kuntilanak.

programme.title: Cinta Kembar
programme.desc: Rhoma Irama sukses besar sebagai musikus dangdut. Kedua adiknya, Deddy dan Herry penuh semangat berlatih karena ingin mengikuti jejak sang kakak. Sebagai remaja, keduanya tak lepas dengan masalah asmara. Kakak-beradik ini mempunyai pacar gadis kembar, Ela dan Eli. Pada saat orang tua Ela dan Eli ingin menjodohkan salah satu anak kembarnya dengan pria lain, mereka menolak, karena cinta kedua pasangan itu sudah begitu mendalam. Cobaan Deddy bukan saja datang dari orang tua Eli, tetapi datang pula dari pemuda lain terhadap Eli.

programme.title: Soekarno
programme.desc: Soekarno berperan penting dalam kemerdekaan Indonesia, dengan dibantu sahabat-sahabatnya. Dalam kisah ini juga ada sosok perempuan yang selalu mendukung karir dari soekarno yaitu Inggit dan Fatmawati, konflik juga sempat terjadi dalam kisah asmara Soekarno. Hingga pada akhirnya Indonesia bisa merdeka pada tanggal 17 Agustus 1945 dengan ditandakan pembacaan proklamasi oleh Soekarno.

programme.title: Video Maut
programme.desc: Menceritakan tentang Doni yang memiliki keinginan untuk membuat video mesum dengan kekasihnya Maya di sebuah villa. Maya merupakan gadis lugu yang dikerjai oleh Doni. Di villa itu maya tidak sendiri namun mengajak temanya dan membuat rencana Doni berantakan, akhirnya ia membuat rencana agar teman-teman maya pergi dan melancarkan aksinya. Saat Doni merayu Maya dan memulai membuat video munculah sosok menyeramkan. Doni dan maya akhirnya gila. Video itu tersebar di dunia maya, dan barang siapa yang menontonya akan mati dibunuh oleh sosok menyeramkan di video itu.

programme.title: Pantai Selatan
programme.desc: Mengisahkan dendam Lastri yang mati karena dipaksa menikah saat kondisinya tengah hamil dan jatuh ke jurang goa blorong. Ular besar menolong anak Lastri dan mengasuhnya hingga dewas. Anak tersebut bernama Larasati yang wujudnya cantik hingga membuat banyak orang menggodanya, namun setiap orang yang menggodanya akan mati dikarenakan dendam ibunya yang belum terlaksana.

programme.title: Tabah Sampai Akhir
programme.desc: Bercerita tentang tiga anak yatim piatu yang berangkat ke Jakarta untuk mencari pamannya. Ternyata Jakarta memang keras, mereka mengalami kesulitan-kesulitan, seperti ditipu. Lalu mereka ditolong Hadi hingga bisa menemukan pamannya. Tetapi kemudian mereka mengalami kecelakaan yanga membuat pamannya tewas, sementara mereka bertiga jadi cacat seperti gagu, pincang dan buta. Setelah menjadi gelandangan, mereka masing2 diadopsi hingga bisa menjadi Pesilat, dokter dan pianis.

programme.title: Kutukan Arwah Santet
programme.desc: Film ini bercerita tentang kisah terbunuhnya seorang gadis yang menyimpan misteri. Beberapa tahun setelah kematiannya, arwah gadis ini pun kerap merasuki tubuh Kirana dan menimbulkan korban. Suatu hari, penyebab kematian gadis ini pun terkuak.

programme.title: Nada-Nada Rindu
programme.desc: Ramlan merasa kalah bersaing dengan Rhoma Irama. Ia berusaha merusak hubungan Rhoma Irama dengan kekasihnya, Mia. Rhoma difinah berselingkuh dengan Maya, kekasih Ramlan.

programme.title: Sang Pencerah
programme.desc: Sepulang dari Mekah, Darwis muda mengubah namanya menjadi Ahmad Dahlan. Seorang pemuda usia 21 tahun yang gelisah atas pelaksanaan syariat Islam yang melenceng ke arah sesat, Syirik dan Bid'ah.

programme.title: Kuntilanak 3
programme.desc: Samantha yang memiliki misi pribadi untuk mencabut wangsit yang ia miliki berupa kekuatan untuk memanggil kuntilanak bertemu dengan rombongan Darwin, Asti, Herman dan Petra yang mencari 2 orang temannya yang hilang di desa Ujung Sedo. Halangan dan rintangan harus dihadapi oleh Samantha demi menuntaskan misinya.

programme.title: Ganesha
programme.desc: Ganesha, pemuda daerah yang mencoba mengadu nasib di kota, karena atas pengaruh temannya. Pada saat perjalanan, ia berhasil menggagalkan aksi pembajakan di bis yang ia tumpangi. Sang supir pun berterima kasih kepadanya dan mengangkatnya anak.

programme.title: Ratu Kostmopolitan
programme.desc: Tiga cewek cantik dan bokek mau tidak mau harus jumpalitan, putar otak, dan baca mantra buat mengusir preman yang mau menggusur rumah kost mereka. Sambil rebutan cowok, pula!

programme.title: Pesan Dari Surga
programme.desc: Grup band beraliran rock, Topeng, yang seluruh personilnya beranggotakan lima anak muda, menghadapi berbagai problem cinta. Ketika permasalahan nyaris meledak, seorang korban kecelakaan yang selamat ini dalam kondisi koma tiba-tiba sadar dan membawa berbagai pesan dari surga.

programme.title: Hattrick
programme.desc: Bercerita tentang turnamen futsal internasional. Kebetulan tahun ini diadakan di Indonesia, maka dicarilah pemain-pemain terbaik dari seulurh Indonesia untuk dididik dan diikutkan dalam turnamen ini.

programme.title: Belahan Jiwa
programme.desc: Cerita tentang empat sahabat yang selalu setia bersama, dan ternyata mereka semua berhubungan dengan pria yang sama

programme.title: Ayat-Ayat Adinda
programme.desc: Menceritakan tentang Adinda yang tinggal bersama keluarga yang memiliki pandangan hidup sediri dan lari dari ajaran agama sesunguhnya. Suatu ketika Adinda membrontak dengan ingin mengikuti lomba MTQ disekolahannya. Halangan dari sang Ayah pun datang untuk berhenti mengikuti lomba itu. Lingkungan disekitarpun menjadi curiga terhadap keluarga tersebut, dan hal itu mungkin bisa menjadi ancaman hidup keluarga Adinda.

programme.title: Tiga
programme.desc: Menceritakan tentang masa depan di tahun 2036. Dikisahkan oleh tiga sahabat bernama Alif, Lam dan Mim yang ditemukan dengan situasi dimana mereka harus berjuangan atas kebenaran masing-masing.

programme.title: Arie Hanggara
programme.desc: Kisah nyata setelah warga Jakarta dihebohkan kasus meninggalnya seorang bocah 8 tahun bernama Arie Hanggara akibat penyiksaan orang tuanya.

programme.title: Bangkit Dari Lumpur
programme.desc: Shakira harus berhadapan dengan maut setelah tanpa sengaja menyaksikan pembunuhan yang dilakukan oleh sekelompok orang. Mayat Shakira dibuang di lumpur Sidoarjo dan jantungnya diambil untuk dijual. Setelah itu Arwah Shakira tidak tenang dan bergentayangan demi menuntut balas kepada para pelakunya

programme.title: Curi-Curi Kesempatan
programme.desc: Cerita Andy dan Martin yang dikerjai oleh Robin dan membuat mereka berdua harus menyamar menjadi perempuan dengan maksud melarikan diri. Mereka menyelinap ke dalam rombongan artis yang akan tour. Berharap akan mendapatkan salah satu gadis-gadis itu membuat kelucuan itu terjadi.

programme.desc: Bercerita tentang upaya penjodohan terhadap seorang tetangga baru, yaitu Vina oleh para tetangga-tetangganya karena dikhawatirkan akan membuat suami-suami mereka tidak aman. Banyolan berkisar pada kesalahpahaman yang sengaja diciptakan agar menimbulkan gelak tawa, terlebih lagi dengan hadirnya Doyok dan Kadir.

programme.title: Sunan Kalijaga & Syech Siti Jenar
programme.desc: Bercerita tentang keadaan Majapahit setelah perang Paregreg. Keadaan sangat kacau dan rakyat banyak yang menderita. Lalu muncul masalah lagi, Syech Siti Jenar, wali yang nyeleneh, mengaku sebagai tuhan hingga dianggap menyeleweng dari ajaran Islam dan kemudian dihukum pancung.

Namun dengan dukungan teman-temannya, Azizul dan Sabok, Iwan berhasil mengatasi masalah dan muncul sebagai tulang punggung tim.
